        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The valkruung has 10 shiny blue-gray tendrils that constantly grab at things in the environment. Each tendril can pick up or hold a Tiny object, such as a coin or piece of jewelry, that isn't being worn or carried. If it uses all 10 of its tendrils, the valkruung can carry a single Small object, such as a @item[backpack|phb]. The valkruung can use its tendrils to interact with objects, but it can't use them to wield a weapon. It has advantage on Dexterity (&amp;Reference[skill=SleightofHand]{Sleight of Hand}) checks when using its tendrils and can use its tendrils to disarm opponents (see the Disarming Tendrils reaction).</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
